r a stylish city car from the smart Car range. LSH Auto UK strive to provide the ultimate Mercedes-Benz buying experience, which you can discover first-hand by visiting any of our UK retailers. Our friendly staff are the core of our business, always ready to offer the expertise our customers rely on. Find your nearest Mercedes-Benz or smart Car Dealership here. LSH Auto UK are proud to be part of the Motability Scheme and provide a wide selection of Motability Mercedes-Benz and smart Cars for you to choose from including standard cars with, or without adaptions & Wheelchair Access Vehicles (WAV’s). Motability is the UK’s leading car scheme for disabled people, allowing recipients of Mobility Allowance to become independently mobile without unwanted hassle or financial strain.  Our dedication to customer care goes beyond the forecourt: selected LSH Autos dealerships also act as an authorised Mercedes-Benz after sales provider, where you can find everything from expert servicing to part replacements. Not only this but our five Manchester sites, both Birmingham Central sites & Birmingham Used Cars also offer a comprehensive Cosmetic Repairs service.             Our Latest Approved Used Cars - View All        View Vehicle    2015 Mercedes-Benz E Class  E220 BlueTEC SE 4dr 7G-Tronic  Only £18,780  Find out More         View Vehicle    2016 Mercedes-Benz CLA Class  CLA 220d AMG Line 4dr Tip Auto [Map...  Only £25,480  Find out More         View Vehicle    2017 Mercedes-Benz C Class  C220d Sport Premium 4dr 9G-Tronic  Only £25,280  Find out More         View Vehicle    2016 Mercedes-Benz GLE Class  GLE 63 S 4Matic Premium 5dr 7G-Tron...  Only £74,480  Find out More         View Vehicle    2017 Mercedes-Benz E Class  E220d SE 4dr 9G-Tronic  Only £24,980  Find out More         View Vehicle    2017 Mercedes-Benz E Class  E220d AMG Line Edition 2dr 7G-Troni...  Only £27,480  Find out More         View Vehicle    2016 smart fortwo  1.0 Prime Premium Plus 2dr Auto  Only £8,950  